‚öôÔ∏è 1Ô∏è‚É£ Install Requirements

Run these once:

npm create vite@latest crm-frontend --template react
cd crm-frontend
npm install axios react-hook-form yup @hookform/resolvers tailwindcss
npx tailwindcss init -p


Then update tailwind.config.js:

/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
export default {
  content: ["./index.html", "./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}"],
  theme: { extend: {} },
  plugins: [],
}


And in src/index.css, add:

@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

üß± 2Ô∏è‚É£ src/services/customerService.js

Replace the URL with your real API base path.

import axios from "axios";

// ‚úÖ Change this to match your Spring Boot API
const API_URL = "http://localhost:8080/api/customers";

export const getCustomers = () => axios.get(API_URL);
export const createCustomer = (data) => axios.post(API_URL, data);
export const updateCustomer = (id, data) => axios.put(`${API_URL}/${id}`, data);
export const deleteCustomer = (id) => axios.delete(`${API_URL}/${id}`);

